Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User across all process variants containing it

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + In Call in variants where both activities appear

Name: Total time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait - User in variants that later include Completed + In Call

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait - User grouped by country
